  title: "What Our Subscribers Stopped Doing (and What Happened Next)",
  meta_title: "What Our Subscribers Stopped Doing (and What Happened Next)",
  excerpt: "They didn't add more work. They subtracted it. And their marketing got better.",
  content_type: "deep_dive",
